  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "In Torque imagine that moment when you pushed the door too hard, it swung
    open very rapidly. You just saw the door swung past you very fast, then hit the
    wall with a very loud, \u201CTHUD!\u201D That door has just experienced torque.\r\n\nTo
    engine and car aficionados, it is the performance of a cycled car engine. To
    them, a car with the best acceleration shift is the car with the highest torque
    capacity. That is because torque is the force acting on a rotating body, which
    is done at a certain distance away from its point of origin.\nFormula: \u03C4
    = i\u03B1 where i = moment of inertia and \u03B1 = angular acceleration"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ed9fe41215e4a2c4a9fa581443855244, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: -4890204404628985631, guid: ed9fe41215e4a2c4a9fa581443855244, type: 2}
