  m_text: "Gravitational potential energy is the energy stored with respect to the
    Earth\u2019s gravitational field. But, if there were to be some changes involved.\nFormula:
    U_g = mgy where m = mass, g = acceleration due to gravity and y = height of object
    from the ground"
