  m_text: "Rate of change in object's angular displacement over time. Just like the
    linear velocity, angular velocity also shows the rate of change in an object\u2019s
    position. \nFormula: \u03C9 = \u0394\u03B8 / t where  \u0394\u03B8 = angular
    displacement and t = time."
