  m_text: "A fluid's specific gravity (g_sp) is the ratio of a fluid's density compared
    to a standard fluid density. Mathematically, g_sp = \u03C1/\u03C1_st where \u03C1
    = pressure and  \u03C1_st = standard density used in water. "
