  m_text: "As theorized by Newton, planets and other celestial bodies have their
    paths shaped like conic sections. This theory was eventually proven by Johannes
    Kepler, a mathematician who helped the astronomer Tycho Brahe in his astronomical
    research. Kepler\u2019s calculations. His computations are named by astronomers
    as \u201CKepler\u2019s Laws of Planetary Motion\u201D."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
