      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Rotation and revolution are both key concepts in this topic. They both
    mean alike in some ways, but different as well. Rotation is the spinning movement
    of an object without actually leaving its position, kind of like how a top spins
    as it is being unwind by the rope, or how our planet has night and day. '
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ed9fe41215e4a2c4a9fa581443855244, type: 2}
